934815152.text: "So far as the role of Bif-1 in mitochondrial apoptosis is concerned some reports suggest that Bif-1 activates Bax and loss of Bif-1 suppresses apoptosis XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, while others believe that Bax activates Bif-1 oligomerization XREF_BIBR and oligomeric Bif-1 can cause lipid membrane vesiculation, thus helps apoptosis."
